{"tid":1782254,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京近郊行程討論","createTime":"2019-12-13T19:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T09:09:21.000Z","uid":14224,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3b578de6a8266b900d985894fd837d4daa48acb1","tid":1782254,"uid":14224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T19:58:17.000Z","msg":"黎緊6月去東京打算抽幾日去近郊<br />\n暫時target 呢個地方: 河口湖(2日1夜)，輕井澤，日光，茨城日立海濱公園<br />\n會用 jr東京廣域周遊券(3日pass)<br />\n想請問<br />\n1. 輕井澤一日遊夠唔夠做?<br />\n2. 邊個行程/景點好啲?<br />\n    A. 如果用3日pass，揀河口湖(2日1夜) + 輕井澤/日光/茨城日立海濱公園(即日來回);<br />\n    B. 河口湖去程搭富士急行巴士(2000yen)，第2日回程先用pass，咁就可以去到揀河口湖(2日1夜) + 輕井澤(即日來回) + 日光/茨城日立海濱公園(即日來回)<br />\n3. 河口湖有冇酒店/旅館推介? (因為我6月去，所以應該唔浸温泉)<br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d927999ba01eecb85e3139edb021cf1a6e103cc3","tid":1782254,"uid":14224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e4d631933311c0e0f5fd92a4100e65e2115c22","tid":1782254,"uid":71759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"1. 輕井澤一日夠做 (前提你只去景點，唔去outlet)<br />\n2. 日光一日太趕，輕井澤同茨城日立海濱公園(你6月去日立海濱公園應該冇咩特別)都可以即日<br />\n3. 最好住湖對面個啲，我上次住湖山亭"},{"pid":"42549933d0e0a0aeb9c4f1bfb352b7554f08a6c6","tid":1782254,"uid":113335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:43:18.000Z","msg":"河口湖 住過富士吟景 算平d都睇到逆富士"},{"pid":"34cb9afaf21df4fa6d46203074e8275204600949","tid":1782254,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:02:07.000Z","msg":"點解唔去越後湯澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a17d82aad94091b430b265d43e34a603d409e60","tid":1782254,"uid":14224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34cb9afaf21df4fa6d46203074e8275204600949","tid":1782254,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislik